title: Loving Hut - Malioboro
typeOfFood: Vegan, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Asian, Indonesian, Indonesian
description: Part of international chain of vegan restaurants opened by followers of Supreme Master Ching Hai, an advocate for vege living. Serving all vegan food, coffee, non-alcoholic beverages, and vegan desserts. Each location is individual family owned. Extensive menu, fresh-squeezed juice available. Informal setting with open-air downstairs and air-conditioning upstairs. It's opposite Hotel Ibis Style Jogonegaran.
streetAddress: Jl. Kemetiran Kidul 1, Terusan Jl. Dagen, Malioboro
